description:
Overview:  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Superman/Batman" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Superman/Batman</a>

Contains:

   Superman Batman 001-006 - World's Finest (2003-04) (Digital-1920) (Zone-Empire)
   Superman Batman 007 - Protege (2004) (Digital-1920) (Zone-Empire)
   Superman Batman 008-013 - Supergirl from Krypton (2004|Digital-1920|Zone-Empire)
   Superman Batman 014-018 - Absolute Power (2005) (Digital-1920) (Zone-Empire)
   Superman Batman 019 - New Adventures of Supergirl (2005|Digital-1920|Zone-Empire)
   Superman Batman 020-025 - With a Vengeance (2005-06) (Digital-1920) (Zone-Empire)
   
   Superman Batman 022 (2005) (Kryptonese To English) (ReZam-DCP)
   
   Superman Batman Annual 2006 - Stop Me If You've Heard This One (Beast's Library)
   
Misses:   Superman Batman #26 - #87 (2006 - 2011)
   
   This is the entirety of the Zone-Empire hi-res set.
   
   There is a follow-up hi-res set by JK-Empire, which spans issues #26 - #40, which
   somewhat inexplicably represents the next two-and-a-half story arcs ("Torment" 
   runs from issues #37 - #42), which in turn is what ultimately swayed me to create 
   this torrent out of only the first set and not include part or all of the second 
   set as well. Issues #41 - #87 exist, with a few isolated exceptions, only as 
   traditionally-scanned 0-Days... for the time being and to my knowledge, that is!
